dialogue.name: I'm not one to brag, but... Daaaamn, I am killing it today!
We're keeping the vibes good and groovy today.
Not too bad. Just haven't hit my stride yet.
Okay, that wasn't my best. Guess I'm having an off day, huh?
Work must've taken a toll on me this week. I think I'm due for a 'me' day to get myself back into spirits.
